data.description: ***$5,000.00*** in Closing Cost with full price offer!!!!! Looking for a great starter home near restaurants, parks and shopping, then look no further.  This home is move in ready and sits on a corner lot, with several fruit trees and plenty of yard space for the kids to play with their pets.  The original carport was enclosed and now serves as an awesome family room.  It could easily be converted to bedroom or an office.  The large open space creates several decorative opportunities for the creative homeowner.  You can keep it as a kitchen/dining area or convert it to a formal dining/living area.  There is also a cozy addition that makes a nice sitting area for family time.   The City Permitted roof was replaced in 2009.  The seller is open to working with buyers using down payment programs such as SHIP or Florida Bond.  Please note, window treatments do not convey.  Call today for an appointment.
